What you need to know:

The tourism industry, which employs more than two million people, has been negatively impacted by the global restrictions imposed to curb the spread of the virus and as a result many jobs have been lostThis appointment gives me an opportunity to contribute positivity towards saving millions of jobs and livelihoods in my countryI shall have the pleasure and honour to market Kenya and tell the world that the destination is open and that we have many beautiful locations that everyone can visit and enjoy